ComicInfo.Summary:
In The Freebooters, Axus and his band, hungry for action, raid the Kalif's own palace, only to find things there unsettlingly bizarre. Meanwhile, the situation is getting out of hand back at The Ram and the Peacock. In The Paradoxman, Tristan Caine's treatment at the hands of his increasingly strange psychoanalyst pushes him to the edge -- which way will he fall? In Young Gods, we return to All-Worlds to find Otan and Queen Organa at increasing odds over the intended wedding of Heros and Celestra, while the evil Grand Vizier manipulates the hapless cherubs into doing his very dirty work. Join captivated readers across the globe for the seventh amazing issue of Barry Windsor-Smith: STORYTELLER, an omnibus of wonder that delivers comics entertainment at its best.
